    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% User Access
    %% =====================================================

    Console --> APIGateway
    REST --> APIGateway
    WS --> APIGateway
    CLI --> APIGateway

    %% =====================================================
    %% Gateway Routing
    %% =====================================================

    APIGateway --> Deploy
    APIGateway --> Workflow
    APIGateway --> Policy
    APIGateway --> Scheduler
    APIGateway --> Plugin
    APIGateway --> Secrets

    %% =====================================================
    %% Internal Services
    %% =====================================================

    Deploy --> Workflow
    Deploy --> Policy
    Deploy --> Secrets
    Deploy --> Plugin

    Workflow --> Scheduler
    Workflow --> Policy

    %% =====================================================
    %% Shared Platform Services
    %% =====================================================

    Deploy --> EventBus
    Workflow --> EventBus
    Policy --> EventBus
    Scheduler --> EventBus
    Plugin --> EventBus
    Secrets --> EventBus

    Deploy --> Metadata
    Workflow --> Metadata
    Policy --> Metadata
    Scheduler --> Metadata

    Deploy --> Config
    Workflow --> Config

    EventBus --> Audit
    EventBus --> Observability

    %% =====================================================
    %% Relay Connectivity
    %% =====================================================

    EventBus --> Relay

    Relay <-->|Persistent TLS| Agent

    %% =====================================================
    %% Agent Internals
    %% =====================================================

    Agent --> Runtime
    Agent --> Inventory
    Agent --> Health
    Agent --> ConfigMgr
    Agent --> Executor

    Runtime --> Containers
    Runtime --> Kubernetes
    Runtime --> VM
    Runtime --> WASM

    Executor --> Runtime

    Inventory --> Observability
    Health --> Observability

